  "body_html": "<!DOCTYPE html\n  SYSTEM \"about:legacy-compat\">\n<html lang=\"en-us\" dir=\"ltr\"><head><title>Cash Flow for a Class in a Securities Account</title><meta charset=\"utf-8\"><link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" media=\"screen,projection\" href=\"/resource/css/style-v2.css\"><script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"js/sap-strings.js\"></script></head><body class=\"en-us sap-light centered navigation-default enumeration-disabled\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-container\" class=\"container_12\" role=\"application\"><div id=\"d4h5-section-container\" class=\"grid_12\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-content\" class=\"grid_8 alpha omega\"><section><div class=\"page topic  - topic-topic \" id=\"loio1b19c55368511d4be10000000a174cb4\"><h1 class=\"title topictitle1\">Cash Flow for a Class in a Securities Account </h1><div class=\"body\">\n<p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph emphasis emphasis\">Use</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\">The <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Cash Flow for a Class in a Securities Account</span> (TPM40) report\nprovides a chronological quantity view of the positions. It shows incoming payment flows\nand any tax flows that may have to be generated. The cash flow for a class in a\nsecurities account is based on update types. </p>\n<aside class=\"note\" aria-labelledby=\"n0t\"><div class=\"title\" id=\"n0t\"><strong>Note</strong></div>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"loio1b19c55368511d4be10000000a174cb4__ul_l32_4jy_cpb\">\n<li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">The report does not show any price gains or losses. </p></li>\n<li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">Future cah flows are displayed for the number of years defined in Customizing\nunder <span class=\"ph menucascade\"><img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstart.gif\" alt=\"Start of the navigation path\" title=\"Start of the navigation path\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Treasury and Risk Management</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Transaction Manager</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Securities</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Master Data</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Product Types</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Define Company Code-Dependent Settings for the Product\n                                Type</span><img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navend.gif\" alt=\"End of the navigation path\" title=\"End of the navigation path\"></span> in the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">CM period</span> field for the product\ntype.</p></li>\n</ul></aside>\n<p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph emphasis emphasis\">See also:</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" href=\"2d18da531198434de10000000a174cb4.html\">Cash Flows</a>\n</p>\n</div></div></section><div class=\"clear\"></div>\n</div></div></div></body></html>"
